@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

### Overview — cash balance, transaction count, fees & taxes paid
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/overview

###

### Portfolio — cost basis per asset, total invested, dividends received
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/portfolio

###

### Spending — card spend, transfer outflows, top 10 merchants
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/spending

###

### Income — broken down by type (interest, dividends, bonuses, transfers, etc.)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/dashboard/income
